    'Celiac Disease Serology',
    "A 30-year-old woman has chronic diarrhea, weight loss, iron-deficiency anemia, and an intensely pruritic vesicular rash on her elbows. Duodenal biopsy shows villous atrophy with intraepithelial lymphocytes. Which serologic antibody is the recommended first-line screening test for her underlying disease?",
